---
description: "CI-WATCH: after push/PR updates, poll CI and ingest logs on failure"
alwaysApply: true
---

When a change claims merge-ready OR after updating a PR:
- Run /ci-watch.
- If CI fails: run /ci-fetch-logs and create a Lane I CI-fix task based on artifacts/ci-logs.
- Never wait indefinitely. Use bounded polling only.